title: Lf Duos that put in hours.
body:
Hi im Known As hejibeji... I love to Adc a lot, Looking for a Friend/duo around my skill level wanting to grind with me. Im currently around Mid Silver elo.

My Off role is Top lane. (Rumble).

My Adc pool is decent, we can discuss that more if needed.

I prefer Any duo, but Prefer Jg or Mid Players... Sure Support and Top is Fine. We can work up Grinding hours. I do not mind, im easy. =]
